trigonometric basa: Basa rekona rinotaridzwa sereshiyo yehurefu hwemativi ekona yekona yekurudyi
inverse function: Chiitiko chinowanikwa nekuratidza mutsauko unotsamira werimwe basa sechinhu chakazvimirira cherimwe
cosecant: Reciprocal of the sine function, inotsanangurwa sereshiyo ye hypotenuse kune mhiri kwekona yekona yekona.
cotangent: Kudzokororwa kweiyo tangent basa, rinotsanangurwa sereshiyo yeyakatarisana kune rimwe divi rekona yekona yekurudyi.
trigonometric identity: Kuenzana kunosanganisira mabasa etrigonometric ayo ari echokwadi kune ese mavhezheni
mutemo wesines: Mugonyo nhanhatu, reshiyo yehurefu hwedivi kune sine yekona yaro yakapesana inongogara
mutemo we cosines: Mugonyonhatu, sikweya yedivi yakaenzana nehuwandu hwemakona emamwe mativi maviri kubvisa kaviri chigadzirwa chemativi maviri aya uye cosine yekona yakasanganisirwa.
radian measure: Chiyero chekona mumaradians, inova reshiyo yehurefu hwearc kune radius yayo
arc urefu: Mufambo uri pakati pemapoinzi maviri uchitevedza chikamu che curve
sector: Chikamu chedenderedzwa chakakomberedzwa neradii mbiri uye arc yavo yakavharirwa
trigonometric ratio: Reshiyo yehurefu hwemativi maviri egonyonhatu yekurudyi
trigonometric equation: Equation inosanganisira imwechete kana akati wandei mabasa etrigonometric echinhu chinosiyanisa
